## 1️⃣ What Is Django Admin?

Out of the box, Django gives you a **complete web interface** to create, read, update, and delete any model, manage users and permissions, and search and filter data — all without writing a single line of frontend code.

Just register your model and it appears in admin:

```python
# blog/admin.py
from django.contrib import admin
from .models import Post

admin.site.register(Post)  # Post appears in admin ✅
```

